=\"/index.php/Gunthor_Hightower\" title=\"Gunthor Hightower\">Gunthor Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Hightower\" title=\"Humfrey Hightower\">Humfrey Hightower</a></li></ul>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Mentions\">Mentions</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=The_Forsaken_(The_Winds_of_Winter)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Mentions\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<table class=\"wikitable\" width=\"100%\">\n\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\">\n<td style=\"width:20;\">\n<p><b>Events:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsmoot_on_Old_Wyk\" title=\"Kingsmoot on Old Wyk\">Kingsmoot on Old Wyk</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Doom_of_Valyria\" title=\"Doom of Valyria\">Doom</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Houses:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Ironmaker\" title=\"House Ironmaker\">House Ironmaker</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hewett\" title=\"House Hewett\">House Hewett</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Greyjoy\" title=\"House Greyjoy\">House Greyjoy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Redwyne\" title=\"House Redwyne\">House Redwyne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Codd\" title=\"House Codd\">House Codd</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Myre\" title=\"House Myre\">House Myre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Hightower\" title=\"House Hightower\">House Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tyrell\" title=\"House Tyrell\">House Tyrell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Wynch\" title=\"House Wynch\">House Wynch</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Goodbrother\" title=\"House Goodbrother\">House Goodbrother</a></li></ul>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:25;\">\n<p><b>Places:</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"